AzureBlade opened a frequency with the City. He knew he probably 
wasn't waited for, but that changed nothing.

AzureBlade: Maximal City, this is unit AzureBlade. I am bringing a new 
addition to our forces. Her name is Mistra. I would like the 
assistance of some who is skilled with engineering.

__________________________________________________________
> > <<AzureBlade was glad. He set his feelings apart for now. They 
would 
> > have to get to the base first, and then, maybe, think of the 
future. A 
> > beep in his HUD indicated the city's proximity.
> > 
> > AzureBlade: I detect the base. We should see it... now! Do you see 
> > those golden towers?>>
> 
> Mistra looked ahead, straining to see the base...and spotted the 
glittering 
> golden towers ahead of them. "I can see it!" she replied, almost 
cheerfully. 
> Now she'd find out just who she was...they'd be able to help her!
